name: pylibmc
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.5.1" %}
{% set gh_org = "lericson" %}
{% set gh_repo = "pylibmc" %}

package:
  name: {{ gh_repo }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ gh_repo }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 18fa39885fce5464977d657185f55e491315b84686533db58054605165fd9b06

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - libmemcached
    - python
    - toolchain

  run:
    - libmemcached
    - python

test:
  requires:
    - python
  imports:
    - _pylibmc
    - pylibmc

about:
  home: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Quick and small memcached client for Python

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
